amendatorysection.catchline: State Court Administrator; criminal homicide report; provide forms.
amendatorysection.para: The State Court Administrator shall provide all forms necessary to carry out sections 29-2524.01 and 29-2524.02.

source.note: The repeal of section 29-2524.02 by Laws 2015, LB 268, section 35, is not effective because of the vote on the referendum at the November 2016 general election.
